{"tid":2447683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學中國民運份子《零八憲章》的《2021香港約章》只是一條死路","createTime":"2021-03-15T11:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T00:47:54.000Z","uid":261647,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9beaf2a511e1b8b8d02d96fbe2ecd53d4e23acd6","tid":2447683,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:01:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10159000745682357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10159000745682357&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=7493f6ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10159000745682357</a><br />\n<br />\n民運份子班咁既野就唔好學啦，睇唔到佢地下場咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10159001486637357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10159001486637357&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=3d93df25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10159001486637357</a><br />\n<br />\n你求的是生存，不是平權，平權團體幫不到你的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1371131506815565825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1371131506815565825&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=ce403605\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1371131506815565825&h=2af5032b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1371131506815565825</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1371317734156374020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1371317734156374020&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=88beff24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1371317734156374020&h=183a4265\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1371317734156374020</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10159001492842357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10159001492842357&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=160ca548\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10159001492842357</a><br />\n<br />\n流亡政府不是重點，重點是流亡預算。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/patrick.yeh.165/posts/10219724628695671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpatrick.yeh.165%2Fposts%2F10219724628695671&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=bf5b5b5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/patrick.yeh.165/posts/10219724628695671</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYqXCV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYqXCV6.jpg&h=075a3080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n<br />\n個人建議：<br />\n香港篇：<br />\n依主權在民原則（主權屬於在地人民）糾正制度（即真民主）<br />\n爭取全自治（即外交完全自主、軍事完全自主、完整國際地位、三權不在中國之下）<br />\n重新立憲<br />\n承諾完成前面之後實現轉型正義<br />\n切法給予香港有經濟困難的同路人經濟支援，並創立或找經濟來源<br />\n罷工之時有海外幫助罷工<br />\n研討超限戰<br />\n<br />\n中國篇：<br />\n聯合各受壓迫民族和群體<br />\n討論和制定分治詳情<br />\n各板塊和文化圈可以以邦聯、各式同盟（軍事、聯防、能源等等）、國際條約等等解決合作問題用以取代吞併和一元化，這要討論<br />\n<br />\n國際篇：<br />\n協助台灣不被中國吞併<br />\n尊重台灣人國家正常化的意願，這要加以推廣<br />\n倡議對中國禁運（制裁作用其實不大，但至於出兵，各國國內又未到這程度，如果某國已經向中國實施制裁，則下一步可倡議禁運。以前二戰時美國對大日本帝國、冷戰時自由國家對蘇聯，都有實施禁運，結果可見。）<br />\n<br />\n另外：<br />\n殖民地人民公投自決殖民地前途，係人權，就算中國未「分治」，都係可以向國際爭取認同、協助舉辦並幫助實踐結果。<br />\n<br />\n台灣獨立運動是從中華民國獨立，不是從中華人民共和國獨立，實質上做的是國家正常化。１、放在中國篇是對台灣人非常無禮。２、台灣人無須用「自決」達成國家正常化。"},{"pid":"3d28be5ee65b32d15d4ceb9848e8fd22dac4327f","tid":2447683,"uid":5502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"唔爭取獨立即係晒氣"},{"pid":"f68ea8ff7c17946ede4a2ed3abc202b42297646b","tid":2447683,"uid":263349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"2021香港約章 點解好似無乜人討論？"},{"pid":"bf565ab0b2032ac29b087531021c24f2de9fd17b","tid":2447683,"uid":47202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f68ea8ff7c17946ede4a2ed3abc202b42297646b","tid":2447683,"uid":263349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"2021香港約章 點解好似無乜人討論？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:28:22.000Z","msg":"你如果睇過份垃圾左膠憲章，你都唔會想討論。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea9b5c8ad33c81c429e17b52ef37abe9bb3cc7c","tid":2447683,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:47:54.000Z","msg":"609 612果陣冇錢銀反而有士氣（背水一戰）<br />\n一旦涉及錢銀反而忘記初心爾虞我詐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}